2026-07-08 01:11:29,059 INFO seed.core.tool_runtime: Executing tool (async): file_edit with args: {'filepath': '/home/u2/agent/codeagent/codeagent/web/static/body.html', 'new_text': '          <p class="section__desc">\n            预设方案整合了远程地址、SSH 连通性和 PAT 凭据。每个方案就是一整套 Git 远程配置，创建项目时一步到位。\n          </p>\n\n          <!-- Git 远程预设方案（集成版） -->\n          <div style="margin-bottom:var(--sp-3);padding:var(--sp-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;">\n            <select id="selGitDefaultProvider" style="display:none;"></select>\n            <select id="selConfigCredProvider" style="display:none;"></select>\n            <div style="font-weight:500;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">📋 预设方案</div>\n            <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0 0 var(--sp-2);">\n              每个方案包含平台、所有者、主机地址、SSH 连通状态和 PAT 凭据——全套一起管理。\n            </p>\n            <label class="checkbox-row" style="margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">\n              <input type="checkbox" id="chkGitDefaultEnabled"/>\n              <span>新建项目时默认启用远程仓库</span>\n            </label>\n            <div id="gitDefaultsForm" style="display:none;">\n\n              <!-- 方案列表 -->\n              <div id="gitPresetList"></div>\n\n              <!-- PAT 内联表单 -->\n              <div id="gitPatForm" style="display:none;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:var(--sp-2);margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">\n                <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:var(--sp-1);">🔐 PAT 配置 — <span id="patFormHostLabel"></span></div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPatUser">用户名</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpPatUser" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="用户名或邮箱" style="max-width:200px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPatToken">Token / 密码</label>\n                  <input type="password" id="inpPatToken" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="Personal Access Token" style="max-width:250px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="row-actions">\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" id="btnPatSave">保存</button>\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="btnPatCancel">取消</button>\n                  <span id="patFormStatus" class="status-line" style="display:inline;margin-left:8px;"></span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <!-- 方案编辑表单 -->\n              <div id="gitPresetEditor" style="display:none;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:var(--sp-2);margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">\n                <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:var(--sp-1);" id="gitPresetEditorTitle">添加方案</div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPresetName">方案名称</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpPresetName" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="例如: GitHub 主号" style="max-width:200px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="selPresetProvider">平台</label>\n                  <select id="selPresetProvider" class="md-select" style="max-width:160px;">\n                    <option value="github">GitHub</option>\n                    <option value="gitlab">GitLab</option>\n                    <option value="gitee">Gitee</option>\n                    <option value="bitbucket">Bitbucket</option>\n                    <option value="custom">自定义</option>\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row" id="rowPresetHost" style="display:none;">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPresetHost">主机地址</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpPresetHost" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="例如 git.tagword.cn" style="max-width:250px;">\n                  <span class="form-hint">选「自定义」时必填</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPresetOwner">所有者</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpPresetOwner" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="用户名或组织名" style="max-width:200px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label">协议</label>\n                  <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;">\n                    <label style="font-size:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;cursor:pointer;">\n                      <input type="radio" name="presetProtocol" value="ssh" checked> SSH\n                    </label>\n                    <label style="font-size:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;cursor:pointer;">\n                      <input type="radio" name="presetProtocol" value="https"> HTTPS\n                    </label>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <label class="checkbox-row">\n                  <input type="checkbox" id="chkPresetAutoPush"/>\n                  <span>创建后自动推送初始提交</span>\n                </label>\n                <div class="row-actions" style="margin-top:var(--sp-1);">\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" id="btnPresetSave">保存方案</button>\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="btnPresetCancel">取消</button>\n                  <span id="presetFormStatus" class="status-line" style="display:inline;margin-left:8px;"></span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="btnPresetAdd">+ 添加方案</button>\n            </div>\n          </div>', 'old_text': '          <p class="section__desc">\n            分三块，互不相同：<strong>默认远程</strong>只影响「新建项目」对话框预填；<strong>SSH</strong> 用于 <code>git@host:…</code>；<strong>HTTPS Token</strong> 写入系统凭据助手，供 <code>https://…</code> 拉取/推送。\n          </p>\n\n          <!-- 默认远程配置（仅新建项目预填） -->\n          <div id="gitDefaultsSection" style="margin-bottom:var(--sp-3);padding:var(--sp-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;">\n            <!-- 隐藏的旧字段，供 SSH 读取 -->\n            <select id="selGitDefaultProvider" style="display:none;"></select>\n            <div style="font-weight:500;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">📋 新建项目默认远程方案</div>\n            <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0 0 var(--sp-2);">\n              勾选后，在<strong>新建空白/模板项目</strong>时自动预填方案内的平台、所有者、协议。可保存多套方案随时切换，克隆已有 URL 的项目不会用到此项。\n            </p>\n            <label class="checkbox-row" style="margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">\n              <input type="checkbox" id="chkGitDefaultEnabled"/>\n              <span>新建项目时默认启用远程仓库</span>\n            </label>\n            <div id="gitDefaultsForm" style="display:none;">\n\n              <!-- 方案列表 -->\n              <div id="gitPresetList"></div>\n\n              <!-- 方案编辑表单 -->\n              <div id="gitPresetEditor" style="display:none;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:var(--sp-2);margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">\n                <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:var(--sp-1);" id="gitPresetEditorTitle">添加方案</div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPresetName">方案名称</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpPresetName" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="例如: GitHub 主号" style="max-width:200px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="selPresetProvider">平台</label>\n                  <select id="selPresetProvider" class="md-select" style="max-width:160px;">\n                    <option value="github">GitHub</option>\n                    <option value="gitlab">GitLab</option>\n                    <option value="gitee">Gitee</option>\n                    <option value="bitbucket">Bitbucket</option>\n                    <option value="custom">自定义</option>\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row" id="rowPresetHost" style="display:none;">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPresetHost">主机地址</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpPresetHost" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="例如 git.tagword.cn" style="max-width:250px;">\n                  <span class="form-hint">选「自定义」时必填</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpPresetOwner">所有者</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpPresetOwner" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="用户名或组织名" style="max-width:200px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label">协议</label>\n                  <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;">\n                    <label style="font-size:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;cursor:pointer;">\n                      <input type="radio" name="presetProtocol" value="ssh" checked> SSH\n                    </label>\n                    <label style="font-size:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;cursor:pointer;">\n                      <input type="radio" name="presetProtocol" value="https"> HTTPS\n                    </label>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <label class="checkbox-row">\n                  <input type="checkbox" id="chkPresetAutoPush"/>\n                  <span>创建后自动推送初始提交</span>\n                </label>\n                <div class="row-actions" style="margin-top:var(--sp-1);">\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" id="btnPresetSave">保存方案</button>\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="btnPresetCancel">取消</button>\n                  <span id="presetFormStatus" class="status-line" style="display:inline;margin-left:8px;"></span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="btnPresetAdd">+ 添加方案</button>\n\n              <div class="row-actions" style="margin-top:var(--sp-1);">\n                <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" id="btnGitDefaultsSave">保存所有方案</button>\n                <span id="gitDefaultsStatus" class="status-line" style="display:inline;margin-left:8px;"></span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- SSH 密钥管理（可折叠） -->\n          <div style="margin-top:var(--sp-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;">\n            <div id="gitConfigSshHeader" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:var(--sp-2) var(--sp-3);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;font-size:12px;">\n              <span>🔑 SSH 密钥</span>\n              <span id="gitConfigSshIcon" style="font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);">▶</span>\n            </div>\n            <div id="gitConfigSshBody" style="display:none;padding:0 var(--sp-3) var(--sp-3);">\n              <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0 0 var(--sp-2);">\n                新建项目选 <strong>SSH</strong> 协议时使用。检测目标与上方「默认远程」平台一致，密钥列表来自 <code>ssh -G</code>（与 <code>git push</code> 实际行为一致），连通性 ✅ 即表示可用。\n              </p>\n              <div id="gitConfigSshStatus" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);padding:4px 0;">展开后检查</div>\n              <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;">\n                <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--xs" id="btnConfigSshGen">生成密钥</button>\n                <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--xs" id="btnConfigSshCat">查看公钥</button>\n                <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--xs" id="btnConfigSshTest">测试连接</button>\n              </div>\n              <pre id="gitConfigSshOutput" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text);padding:6px 0;max-height:120px;overflow-y:auto;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;margin:0;"></pre>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- HTTPS 凭据（可折叠） -->\n          <div style="margin-top:var(--sp-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;">\n            <div id="gitConfigCredHeader" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:var(--sp-2) var(--sp-3);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;font-size:12px;">\n              <span>🔐 HTTPS 凭据</span>\n              <span id="gitConfigCredIcon" style="font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);">▶</span>\n            </div>\n            <div id="gitConfigCredBody" style="display:none;padding:0 var(--sp-3) var(--sp-3);">\n              <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0 0 var(--sp-2);">\n                仅在选择 <strong>HTTPS</strong> 协议时需要。Token 存入 <code>git credential</code>（如 macOS 钥匙串），与上方「默认远程」里的平台/所有者无关。\n              </p>\n              <div id="gitConfigCredStatus" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);padding:4px 0;">展开后查看状态</div>\n              <div id="gitConfigCredForm" style="display:none;margin-bottom:var(--sp-2);">\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="selConfigCredProvider">平台</label>\n                  <select id="selConfigCredProvider" class="md-select" style="max-width:160px;">\n                    <option value="github">GitHub</option>\n                    <option value="gitlab">GitLab</option>\n                    <option value="gitee">Gitee</option>\n                    <option value="bitbucket">Bitbucket</option>\n                    <option value="custom">自定义</option>\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpConfigCredUrl">凭据主机 URL</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpConfigCredUrl" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="https://github.com" style="max-width:250px;" readonly/>\n                  <span class="form-hint">由平台自动填充，对应 git 凭据里的 host</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpConfigCredUser">用户名</label>\n                  <input type="text" id="inpConfigCredUser" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="用户名或邮箱" style="max-width:200px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-row">\n                  <label class="form-label" for="inpConfigCredToken">Token / 密码</label>\n                  <input type="password" id="inpConfigCredToken" class="form-input-sm" placeholder="Personal Access Token" style="max-width:250px;">\n                </div>\n                <div class="row-actions">\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" id="btnConfigCredSave">保存凭据</button>\n                  <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="btnConfigCredCancel">取消</button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;">\n                <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--xs" id="btnConfigCredAdd">+ 添加凭据</button>\n                <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--xs" id="btnConfigCredShow">查看已存储</button>\n                <button type="button" class="btn btn--ghost btn--xs" id="btnConfigCredClear">清除所有</button>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>'}
